		<title>智慧型手機製造商小米推出首款電動車</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/zh-hans/analysis/market-news/smartphone-maker-xiaomi-launches-its-first-electric-vehicles</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 09:24:48 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[市场新闻及观点]]></category>
